<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer13591722865260062635">Penelope Williamson is an internationally renowned author of historical romance and suspense. Penelope Williamson was born in Fairbanks, Alaska, and spent the first eleven years of her life as an US Air Force brat. She has a B.A. in history, an M.A. in broadcast journalism, and was in the U.S. Marine Corps for six years, where she reached the rank of Captain. She has more than 1.8 million books in</span>
  <span id="freeText13591722865260062635" style="display:none">Penelope Williamson is an internationally renowned author of historical romance and suspense. Penelope Williamson was born in Fairbanks, Alaska, and spent the first eleven years of her life as an US Air Force brat. She has a B.A. in history, an M.A. in broadcast journalism, and was in the U.S. Marine Corps for six years, where she reached the rank of Captain. She has more than 1.8 million books in print, including The Outsider, Heart of the West A Wild Yearning, Once in a Blue Moon, and Keeper of the Dream. Penny is a past winner of the Romantic Times' Best Historical Romance of the Year award and the Romance Writers of America's RITA awards. Penelope Williamson lives with her husband in Mill Valley, California.<br /><br /><br /><b>pseudonyms:</b> <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/59933.Elizabeth_Lambert" title="Elizabeth Lambert" rel="nofollow noopener">Elizabeth Lambert</a>, <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/4714589.Penn_Williamson" title="Penn Williamson" rel="nofollow noopener">Penn Williamson</a></span>
  <a data-text-id="13591722865260062635" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

</div>
